CASTING NOTICE — VANCOUVER
Seeking** cool looking, camera-friendly adults** (all adult ages welcome) **based in Vancouver** for a short shoot.

**WHEN:** November 4
**WHERE:** Outdoor spots around Stanley Park (exact meet point shared upon booking), and potentially indoors as well at a studio.
**SCENES:** Relaxed, music-centric visuals — reclining in scenic nature locations and listening to music

**bright colors in your own wardrobe (you need to come camera ready) is a plus!

**RATE:** **$150** for **2–3 hours**

**TO APPLY:** Email **mylcasting@gmail.com** with:
* Your name and age
* A recent photo (waist-up or full-body)
* A brief note on availability and any on-camera experience (optional)

Local Vancouver applicants only. No acting experience required.

** **

**18 Mini serial wojenny 1940 historyczny z elementami Fantazy**

** **

**Oficer francuski -  mężczyzna**

Nasza Gliwicka Grupa Pasjonatów ‘’Grupa1940’’ poszukuje ** mężczyznę** **bez zarostu w obwodzie klatki 95 –105 cm, pas: 85 – 95 cm** w **wieku 20 – 50** lat do roli oficera francuskiego .Szukamy kogoś mieszkającego w **Gliwic lub okolic**: Zabrze, Katowice najdalej gdyż odległość do tej roli ma znaczenie. Kostium jest już zrobiony na konkretny wymiar a osoba grająca tego oficera będzie zmiennikiem innego o podobnych parametrach. Same zdjęcia będą realizowane na terenie Gliwic. Szykujemy się do kilku scen bitewnych z francuzami. Kilka postaci ma nieduże kwestie po francusku.

 

W tym roku będziemy realizować mini serial oparty o wątki grupy okultystycznej ’’**Ahnenerbe’**’ która chce zdobyć słynne artefakty ale w tym ktoś im chce przeszkadzać. Wstępnie mamy zamiar zrobić 6 odcinków po 10/15 min. Będziemy też sukcesywnie dodawać inne ogłoszenia związane z tym projektem. Mile widziane zdjęcia aktualne. Nasze plany filmowe są układane głównie w jakieś dni weekendowe z wyprzedzeniem 1 2 tygodni. **Nie będzie to zlecenie płatne.**

 

Od 01.04.25 założyliśmy swój kanał na portalu youtube z filmami z naszych planów żeby można było zobaczyć jak to u nas wygląda od kuchni. 

 

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCE8KyfwpyFGzzwUDqdwy74g

 

**Nie będzie to zlecenie płatne.**

 

Więcej informacji na Priv

**Serial nie jest stworzony z sympatii do tej nazistowskiej organizacji lecz wynika to z samego scenariusza aby ukazał zbrodnie i sam fakt iż była w pełni zła. W produkcji znajdą się osoby, które będą chcieć walczyć i potępiać te wielkie zło jakim był nazizm. W oparciu o Dz.U.2017.0.2204 t.j. - Ustawa z dnia 6 czerwca 1997 r. - Kodeks karny,Art. 256 "Propagowanie faszyzmu lub innego ustroju totalitarnego lub nawoływanie domnienawiści", §3 - nie narusza prawa proponując przedmiot do celów historycznych lub kolekcjonerskich.**

Do projektu fotograficznego szukam młodych osób w wieku 16-22 lata - dowolna sylwetka, typ urody i wzrost.

Szczególnie poszukuję umięśnionych chłopaków/sportowców, modeli/modelek plus size i grup przyjaciół.

Zdjęcia w Warszawie w listopadzie/grudniu 2025, dokładny termin do ustalenia. Sama sesja potrwa pół godziny.

items.title: casting call

items.text:
Hello, 
We are looking for two performers to act in a short movie. “Where the Light Shines” explores denial, anxiety, and female identity in a male-dominated society. The film reflects the tension between masculine and feminine energy – control and surrender – and how these forces collide in the face of inner truth.
The story uses contemporary movement and dance to showcase the troubled inner-word of the characters. You will be working closely with the director and choreographer to shape the narrative.
Females, non-binary and all ethnicities is encouraged to apply!<3 This is a third year Bachelor project.  
If you are ready to move with the lights, contact us at: edsh.production@gmail.com.

message.text:
Wow 😍💫This must be what it feels like for a dancer to step into a land of music — like Austria, where the spirit of Mozart, Strauss, and Schubert still lingers in the air. 🎻✨
Every moment here feels like it’s wrapped in melody.
💥Don't miss the magical and charming experience of a live performance.
👉Visit https://1kb.link/WCFkYe for information on theatres near you.

items.text:
Genre: Romance/Drama

Logline: Soulmates bound from the beginning of time must navigate the blurred lines between dreams and reality to discover their destiny together.

Roles:

Atlas: 20s, Male

Atlas always feels the weight of the world on his shoulders. He understands more about life and the universe than most people, which doesn’t help his abilities to strike up a conversation and ends up making him look reserved and detached. Atlas feels everything from the rotation of the Earth to everything that is supposed to happen in the future. His connection with the world makes him patient, almost seeming like he is unable to act on his desires, because he knows what the future holds.

Luna: 20s, Female

Luna enjoys the complexities of figuring out what life is. She wants to follow her passions and figure out what they mean along the way. She isn’t the type to turn people away, but instead see what they change in her life. She is never afraid, takes her own mortality in her hands, and believes there is a right answer to everything. The spark of life is in her and she doesn’t want to let anything snuff it out. Her dreams start to show her the past and what the future holds for her.

Pierce: 20s, Male

Pierce is a constant. He is dating Luna. He never does anything unexpected. He has a very simplistic view of the world and events that occur outside of it don’t really concern him. He is steadfast in his decisions and never doubts who he is or what he is doing. You can always expect him to be around, but if things get deeper he will very quickly drown from the weight of his inexperience.

Production Company: pearscarfproductions

Writer/Director: Nathan Chelf

Cinematographer: Nate Coberly

Production Type: Independant

Contact Info: pearscarfproductions@gmail.com

Run Time: Short Film

Compensation: Negotiable, this is a low budget, self funded project.

Union Status: Non-Union

Audition Information: We will be holding in person auditions this Saturday, October 25th from 9:00 AM until 2:00 PM at 3111 E Colfax Ave Denver, CO 80206. Please email us if you are interested and we will get you a time slot. If you are unable to make it in person please reach out and we will set up a virtual audition another time or send you information to do a self tape. For in person we would love to see a monologue and we will have you do cold readings from the script.

Shooting Schedule: We are planning to be filming in December, final dates will be confirmed based on the schedules of our cast.

Filming Locations: The Denver Metro Area

Thank you for taking the time to read through this and I hope to hear from you soon!

# Improvised Filmmaking Workshop in Berlin
## One week to go!

Actors & Directors: Ready to create powerful scenes spontaneously? ✨

Explore the magic of actor-director collaboration in our **Improvised Filmmaking Workshop**.

This hands-on weekend intensive is for all levels. We’ll explore the creation of compelling stories together, building trust, and finding freedom in your craft.

## 🗓️ **UPCOMING DATES:**
* Nov 1/2: **Only three spots left**
* Nov 15/16
* Dec 6/7

## **THE LOWDOWN:**

🎬 For Actors & Directors (all levels)

🇬🇧  In English

⏰ Sat & Sun, 10:00 – 19:00

📍 Reflektor Neukölln

Read what past participants have to say: reviews available on my website!

Don't miss out.

#FilmmakingWorkshop #ActorWorkshop #DirectorWorkshop #ImprovisedFilmmaking #BerlinCreatives #BerlinFilm #BerlinActors #BerlinDirectors #Neukölln #ReflektorNeukölln #WorkshopBerlin #IndieFilmmaking #Improv #SceneStudy #Collaboration

🎬 **Casting-Aufruf – Schauspielerin für die Rolle einer Ermittlerin gesucht**

Für meinen Kurzserien-Dreh **„Der Übersetzer“ (Staffel 1)** suche ich eine **Schauspielerin** für die Rolle einer **Ermittlerin**.

📍 **Drehort:** Koblenz
📅 **Drehtage:** 21.11.2025, 22.11.2025, 23.11.2025, 01.12.2025 und 07.12.2025

**Anforderungen:**
* Alter: **30–40 Jahre**
* Schauspielerische Erfahrung in Film/TV von Vorteil
* Verlässlichkeit und Teamgeist

💶 **Vergütung:** Gage nach Vereinbarung
🏨 **Unterkunft, Verpflegung und Transport** werden von der Produktion übernommen.

📩 **Bewerbung:**
Bitte sende deine Bewerbung mit **kurzem Profil, zwei aktuellen Fotos** und (falls vorhanden) einem **Showreel-Link** an:
**ahmaddirector2@gmail.com**

Vielen Dank – ich freue mich auf eure Bewerbungen!

attachments.ocrText: Kan være et billede af tekst, der siger "STATISTER SOGES Vi soger statister til at spille politibetjente uden replikker til en spillefilm produceret af PIGS UNITE Optagelse: mandag d. 27. oktober (mulig option torsdag d. 30. oktober) Location: Veerlose Tidspunkt: Forvent et tidsrum mellem 7：00-17：00 7：00- 7:00 Vi soger 4 statister alderen 25-45 Honorar: 500DKK Er du interesseret? Sả send en mail til GKIK.Statistkordinator@hotmail.com Dit Navn Alder Et nyere foto (portreet) Tlf. nr. Skriv gerne om bade du kan mandag d. 27. oktober og torsdag d. 30. Vi haber at hore fra dig"

items.text:
Til min kortfilm Banana Ice, der er støttet af Odense Filmværksted, søger jeg to kvindelige spillere til venindeparret Rikke og Sika - spillealder 19-20.

Banana Ice handler om:

Den 18-årige Val, der i starten af historien får nedtur på efter hun, ved ankomst til baren, finder ud af at hendes veninder har ditchet hende. 

Men det bliver faktisk bare held-i-uheld, for hun ender med en aften på bar med venindeduoen Rikke og Sika.

Da de to veninder, sent på aftenen, går ud for at spice øllene op og narkopolitiet kort efter kommer ind, ender Val i et dilemma.

Hun redder hendes “nye” veninders røv, men i panik og for at redde deres egen røv, kaster Sika og Rikke hende under bussen.

Kortfilmen hedder som den gør, fordi en vape, med den smag, er gennemgående motif i historien.

Praktisk:

Kortfilmen optages i Svendborg den 29. og 30. november i dagstimerne - så der er selvfølgelig forplejning. 

Er du og måske din veninde interesseret?

Så send en mail til majamus23@gmail.com med emnet Venindeduo_BananaIce

I mailen kunne jeg godt tænke mig:

* en video af dig/jer, der som de to veninder skal få den sidste ved bordet til at købe drikkevarer til jer - det kan f.eks. være via en løgn, en leg, at stjæle eller noget helt andet.

* har du/I en showreel eller links til andet I har lavet, så send det gerne med.

* en kort, kort præsentation af dig/jer.

Her kommer lidt om veninderne:

Rikke&Sika

Sammen er de den uovervindelige venindeduo.

Man ved, ser man den ene et sted, så er den anden lige om hjørnet.

De er det kvindelige modsvar til det heteroseksuelle forholds tosomhed.

Noget både jeg og Val er misundelige på.

De er spændende og fascinerende mennesker, man ønsker at dele en aften med.

 

Sika

Hendes forældre er succesfulde, så hun kommer fra et hjem hvor der bliver forventet noget af en.

Kærligheden er ikke ubetinget, man skal præstere og gøre sig umage, før man får et klap på skulderen eller en belønning.

 

At være uartig eller opfører sig dårligt fører naturligvis til konsekvenser.

Sika finder nydelse i at være meget langt fra sine forældre, men hjemmet har klart givet hende en hårdhed.

 

Rikke

Hun har en enlig mor, inden hende og Sika blev en tosomhed, var Rikke og hendes mor det.

Hun trives godt i det kvindelige selskab og elsker fællesskab og andre menneskers samvær. Derfor former hun sig også meget efter de mennesker hun er sammen med, så hun altid passer ind og kan være en del af de sociale.

Glæder mig til at se jeres mails <33

Kh Maja, manus/instruktør

We’ve got lots of work coming up for the right people. We’re based mainly in London & Essex, but we deliver parties and events all over the UK. ✨

items.text:
Hi all! I just wanted to introduce myself and share a photos of what I look like 

I’m brand new to this and would die for some advices I want to become a actor. I can do voices and accents I can do my own stunts and fight senses. 

If anyone can point me in a direction where I can share my reals or how I could start would really appreciate it 

FYI the last photo is when I was a extra in Vera it’s why I want to do this more 

Thank you

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of one or more people and beard
May be a black-and-white image
No photo description available.

topComments.text:
This all depends on if you want to do TV/Film or theatre.

Either way, know this.

- Yes, anyone can become an actor, however its an extremely hard industry and most never make a living from it.
- Yes, some people have become successful without training, however attending workshops and short courses will help more than you think.
- Get used to being rejected. 9/10 auditions you go for, you will probably not get. Always ask for feedback and don’t take it personally.
- students are your friends! There are so many student films/indie films out there who are crying out for actors.

Lastly, if you’re ultimately have a back up career plan! Don’t be too quick to quit the day job.

Hope this helps
Wow you were an extra in Vera, that's lush! I think it's YOU, sir, who needs to give us tips!

message.text:
If you're interested in studying at Leeds Arts University, you can find out more about our undergraduate courses at our open days in November! 

Book your place on up to three course talks, including our new courses in BA (Hons) 3D Design and Craft, BA (Hons) Creative Industries Management, BSc (Hons) Creative Technologies, and BA (Hons) Digital Marketing. 

Book your place at https://www.leeds-art.ac.uk/

Hope to see you there!

Hey there Everyone. RJ Castro,  Santa Cruz, CA.  Before I got into Acting, I was a soccer player and coach in San Jose,CA. As well as I am a Chef.

 So I like to think I can give a little Kick, and a little spice or flavor to any role you might have in mind.

 Would love to work with you. Can't wait to see you on set. Available and ready to work. Reel Credit: Produced by Sunny Creative Sunny Creative, Van Nuys, CA . 

RJ Castro
🎭 Actor | Santa Cruz / Bay Area
IMDb: https://imdb.me/rjcastro-sj
Backstage: https://www.backstage.com/u/rjcastro-sj/
IG: https://www.instagram.com/rjcastro.sj

items.summary:
Hey there Everyone. RJ Castro,  Santa Cruz, CA.  Before I got into Acting, I was a soccer player and coach in San Jose,CA. As well as I am a Chef.

 So I like to think I can give a little Kick, and a little spice or flavor to any role you might have in mind.

 Would love to work with you. Can't wait to see you on set. Available and ready to work. Reel Credit: Produced by Sunny Creative Sunny Creative, Van Nuys, CA . 

RJ Castro
🎭 Actor | Santa Cruz / Bay Area
IMDb: https://imdb.me/rjcastro-sj
Backstage: https://www.backstage.com/u/rjcastro-sj/
IG: https://www.instagram.com/rjcastro.sj

items.text:
Experienced comedic & dramatic stage actor, film background/extra & Musical Theatre performer & experienced pro solo personality vocalist with 20 years performing experience in West End Variety, national theatre tours & 5* wedding venues as Singing Waiter 🥰🤩🥳🎬🎭🎤🎸🙌

Major Credits include: 
Sunday Night Live at Her Majesty’s Theatre 2006
The Show Must Go On National Theatre Tour 2008
Open Mic UK Finalist 2016, 2018 & 2019
Mary Queen of Scots feature film extra 2018
Everybody’s Talking About Jamie feature film featured extra 2019
Passenger’s “Remember to Forget” official music video featured extra 2020

Checkout my home scripted monologue self tape except from “The In Link” - role of Aaron below - - 🥰😁🎬🎭🙌

DM, text/WhatsApp or email for castings & booking enquiries & dates/availability - - 
Mob: 07852116434 
Email: jamcon1981@gmail.com
Official James T Wilde Website: 
https://www.jtwildemusic.com

🔥 “Red & Black Elegance” – VIP Models Ibiza 🔥

Confidence isn’t about being seen — it’s about being remembered.

Our models embody power, elegance, and timeless style in every frame. 🖤❤️

✨ Do you have what it takes to represent VIP Models Ibiza on an international stage?

Now is your moment. Join our global casting and become part of the elite.

📲 Apply today through our official website:
🌐 www.vip-models-ibiza.com

💃 Be bold. Be iconic. Be unforgettable.

🌟 KIND REGARDS,
🌿 VIP MODELS IBIZA 
🌴Where Talent Meets Luxury Worldwide

❤️ GLOBAL SERVICES ❤️
✨ Elite Models & Brand Ambassadors
🌍 Worldwide Luxury Travel Curator
🎯 Personalized Bespoke Experiences

📧 Enquire: contact@vip-models-ibiza.com
📲 24/7 WhatsApp Booking: +34 642 906 659

🏝️ OUR COLLABORATING NETWORK:
🌐 VIP Models Ibiza - www.vip-models-ibiza.com
🌴 Max Ibiza - www.maxibiza.com 
✈️ Max Lux Travel - www.maxlux-travel.com
💫 Creating Unforgettable Experiences Across the Globe 💫

———————————————————

items.text:
Hello everyone,

My name is Kayuran and I’m currently working on my first short mobile horror film. The script is in progress, and I’m looking for passionate people who would like to join me on this creative journey.

I’m specifically looking for:
🎬 A professional film editor
🎥 A camera operator (based in Durban/Chatsworth area)

The goal is to work together as a team and create something special. This project isn’t about making money — it’s about sharing stories and giving audiences an enjoyable and memorable film experience.

If you’re interested in being part of this project or know someone who might be, please feel free to reach out. Let’s build something amazing together!

From 
KM PICTURE

CASTING CALL OUT - VANCOUVER

We’re seeking a parent with **two young children (ages 2–6)** who are **comfortable on camera** for a short social media spot.

Will be a feel-good shot in a beautiful **indoor conservatory** in central Vancouver.

**WHEN:** November 4
**WHERE:** Indoor conservatory (Vancouver) — exact address shared upon booking
**SCENES:** Enjoying a music-listening device together and exploring plants with a sense of wonder
**RATE:** **$150 per person** (parent + each child), **up to 2 hours**

**TO APPLY:** Email **mylcasting@gmail.com** with:
* Your name and your children’s ages
* A recent photo of all three of you (separate or together is fine)
* A brief note on availability and on-camera experience (if any)

Local, Vancouver-area applicants only. No acting experience required!

items.text:
*Casting Call for a short dance film shooting early next year January 24th and 25th in VANCOUVER. 
A short dance film expressing the importance of forgiveness of youth, bringing awareness to issues such as mental health, identity struggles and substance addiction in youth culture.
This is a volunteer position, but all food, studio rehearsal space and credits will be provided.
Video clips, photographs and stills will be provided as well for portfolio/demo reels to all dancers.

Requirements:
Must have contemporary dance experience and comfortable in front of camera.
Have reliable transportation to set/rehearsals
Age ranging from 19-27
Must be available BOTH shoot dates and additionally some time before the shoot for rehearsals!

DUE DATE FOR SUBMISSION: NOVEMBER 6TH 
Please submit a headshot/recent photo of yourself and a demo reel or video of your dancing.
Send all applications or questions to:
sodamihong@gmail.com 
shenassakayla@gmail.com

🎶Offering Free VIRTUAL Voice & Acting Lessons!🎶

Hi! I'm Colleen and I'm a music theatre voice teacher, and the owner of Virtuoso Studios. We are proud to have a team of dedicated and experienced teachers who are passionate about helping students discover the joy of music. 

We currently offer lessons in voice, piano, acting, violin, viola, cello, and guitar, along with 2 in person recitals each year in MI, WI, IL, and MO. Each of our teachers is committed to providing personalized instruction to help every student reach their goals. Whether you’re preparing for auditions, looking to grow as a performer, or simply want to enjoy making music, our teachers are here to support and encourage you every step of the way!

Try a free lesson today! This is a great way to meet one of our teachers, experience a lesson, and see how music can be a fun and meaningful part of your life.

If you’d like to get started, fill out this form, and we’ll match you with the teacher who’s the best fit for your goals and interests. [www.virtuosostudios.org/free-trial-lessons](https://www.virtuosostudios.org/free-trial-lessons)

items.summary:
🎶Offering Free VIRTUAL Voice & Acting Lessons!🎶

Hi! I'm Colleen and I'm a music theatre voice teacher, and the owner of Virtuoso Studios. We are proud to have a team of dedicated and experienced teachers who are passionate about helping students discover the joy of music. 

We currently offer lessons in voice, piano, acting, violin, viola, cello, and guitar, along with 2 in person recitals each year in MI, WI, IL, and MO. Each of our teachers is committed to providing personalized instruction to help every student reach their goals. Whether you’re preparing for auditions, looking to grow as a performer, or simply want to enjoy making music, our teachers are here to support and encourage you every step of the way!

Try a free lesson today! This is a great way to meet one of our teachers, experience a lesson, and see how music can be a fun and meaningful part of your life.

If you’d like to get started, fill out this form, and we’ll match you with the teacher who’s the best fit for your goals and interests. [www.virtuosostudios.org/free-trial-lessons](https://www.virtuosostudios.org/free-trial-lessons)
items.title: 🎶Offering Free VIRTUAL Voice & Acting Lessons!🎶

📣 **Szukam osoby do współpracy z lokalem gastronomicznym!** 🍔🥤

Jeśli prowadzisz **TikToka lub Instagrama** z fajnym zasięgiem 📱 — albo jesteś **na dobrej drodze, żeby się rozwinąć** i masz pomysł na ciekawe treści kulinarne — odezwij się do mnie! 🎥✨

Chcemy nawiązać współpracę z kimś, kto:
* jest **kreatywny**,
* potrafi tworzyć **angażujące shorty, reelsy lub relacje**,
* chce **rozwijać się razem z nami** 💪

Oferujemy:
🍽️ współpracę z lokalem o luźnej atmosferze,
🎬 możliwość wspólnego tworzenia materiałów,
🤝 długofalową relację opartą na wzajemnym wsparciu.

📩 Napisz do mnie w wiadomości prywatnej — chętnie porozmawiam o szczegółach!

💖**Zostań Ambasadorką/em naszego studia ruchu! **

💖Chcesz promować **zdrowe podejście do ruchu wśród kobiet 40+** i zachęcać je do aktywności fizycznej? Zgłoś się!

**💖Kogo szukam:**

– twórców UGC

– twórców z **zaangażowaną społecznością kobiet 40+, głównie z Warszawy **(nie szukam „milionowych” zasięgów, liczy się jakość, nie puste liczby)

– osób, które **chcą wejść w tę tematykę** i czują klimat kobiet 40–80+

**Jak się zgłosić:**

👉 wyślij **na priv linki do swoich profili społecznościowych** + napisz coś na temat treści, które tworzysz. 

*(Szczegóły współpracy po wstępnej selekcji.)*

items.text:
# Casting Call: German-Speaking Content Creators (Tech)

We’re a tech brand looking for fluent (native-level) German creators to film simple scripted UGC videos.

**What you’ll do**
* Shoot 2–3 short videos following our provided script (total time on set: ~2–3 hours).
* Self-shoot at home or on location with clean light and clear audio.
* Deliver fast — we move quickly.

**You have**
* Native or near-native German.
* Proven self-shooting experience (UGC, reels, ads, or similar).
* A good camera setup (modern smartphone or mirrorless), tripod, and basic audio.
* Reliable turnaround.

**Compensation**
* From **$150** (TBD based on scope and deliverables).

**What we provide**
* Script + shot list
* Creative notes and framing/safe-zone guidelines

**How to apply**

DANCERS/SINGERS ENTERTAINERS!

Available contracts in 4 and 5-star hotels in the Mediterranean

Summer Season 2026

We are looking for dynamic, confident, and versatile individuals to join our ENTERTAINMENT TEAMS to perform in our PRODUCTION SHOWS at stunning 5-star resorts in Greece from April/may 

Follow the link to see our shows 
production : 

https://youtu.be/9PdbLO--GX4?si=W8fKURLEWPjE9bCG 

WHAT WE OFFER: 
A complete and carefree package including: 

• 3–7 month employment contracts in 5-star and 4-star resorts 

• Competitive net monthly salary based on experience and skills 

• Social security, pension, and accident insurance 

• Free accommodation 

• Three meals per day and beverages in hotel restaurants 

• Flight reimbursement up to €300 

• Stress-free airport transfer to the resort 

• Daily and evening uniforms 

• One day off per week

 • Free training and workshops

• Additional bonuses and commissions, depending on hotel facilities 🌟 

📩Apply Now for Online Auditions ☀️ Send your CV and showreel to: adriano@palmera-agency.com

items.text:
🎬 **CASTING CALL!!** 🎬

A **3-minute application film** is in production — a heartfelt story about a teenage girl who discovers that her mother has cancer. The project explores themes of love, family, and resilience.

**Casting for:**
🌸 **Teen Girl (16–22 years)**
🌼 **Mother (30–45 years)**
🧢 **Boy (10–14 years)**
👔 **Father (30–45 years)**
👥 **Extras / Background actors** (please include your age)

🎬 **Crew members** are also welcome — especially those interested in gaining experience on a small, creative set!

This is a **no-budget film**, but **good food, friendly vibes, and great company** are guaranteed! 🩷🪷

📧 **Interested?** Contact: **[ronyasartplace@gmail.com](mailto:ronyasartplace@gmail.com)**

Let’s create something meaningful together! 💫

items.text:
CASTING CALL FOR A STUDENT SHORT-FILM!

Hi hi! My name is Megan Veto and I am a student at the Aurora Community College and will serve as the Writer/Director of this project. I am in need of actors/actresses for my Production 1 project! This will be unpaid, though I will provide anyone interested with a final version of the film. You will also be fed, so please let me know of any allergies or specific diets you may have!

Title: On the Rocks
Genre: Romantic Comedy
Logline: An angry bride walks into a bar and shakes up Ramos’s day.

SHOOTING DAYS: November 8th (10a - 6p) - 9th (1p - 7p)

LOCATION: 9075 E Lowry Blvd Denver, CO 80230

CHARACTERS:

-Ramos: The bartender. Late 20’s - early 30’s. Calm, cool, and collected. Takes care of his patrons. Wardrobe will be all black and a black button-up shirt.

-Sarah: The angry bride. Mid - late 20’s. Feisty, knows what she wants, but eventually softens under Ramos’s care. Please let me know what your dress size is so I can find a bride’s dress that fits! 😁

-Mike: The ex. Mid - 20’s. Flustered, desperately looking for Sarah. Cheated. Wardrobe will be black slacks and a nice white button-down shirt.

-Ruth: Sarah’s mom. 50’s. Helps Mike look for Sarah. Wardrobe will be a nice dress.

Please email me at megveto96@gmail.com with your headshot and demo reel, I will send you the script to read over.

Thank you so muc

🎙️ **Poszukiwany lektor do krótkiego filmu**

Szukamy **męskiego głosu reklamowego** do podłożenia narracji w **animowanym spocie (ok. 1,5 minuty)**.

**Pole eksploatacji:** internet (spot może być, ale nie musi, wykorzystany w płatnych kampaniach).
**Czas realizacji:** jak najszybciej.
**Kryterium wyboru:** 100% cena.

Zgłoszenia (wycena + próbka nagrania) prosimy wysyłać na adres: **praca@goodeye.com.pl**
W tytule maila wpisz: **„lektor electro”**

Zastrzegamy sobie kontakt z wybranymi osobami.

items.text:
We're seeking an exceptional actor to portray George Harrison in 'A Time To Kill' - our darkly satirical drama exploring the conspiracy surrounding John Lennon's assassination.

The Quiet Beatle speaks. This is a powerful, complex role for an actor ready to bring depth and authenticity to one of music's most iconic figures.

AUDITION DETAILS:

 📅 Friday 24th October 2025 

⏰ 12:00pm - 4:00pm 

📍 @thecasaliverpool Hope Street, Liverpool

 🎭 Playing age: OPEN

TO AUDITION: ✉️ Send CV + recent photo to: howl.michael1963@yahoo.co.uk 🎤 Prepare 2-3 minute monologue of your choice ⏰ You'll be allocated a specific time slot

PRODUCTION: 🎬 Rehearsals: Week of 3rd November (6 weeks) 🎪 Performances: 8th, 9th & 10th December at CASA

This is an exceptional opportunity to be part of a controversial, compelling new work examining one of music history's most significant events.

We welcome performers of all backgrounds and experience levels.

Ready to bring George Harrison to life?

Apply now: howl.michael1963@yahoo.co.uk

#ATimeToKill #CastingCall #GeorgeHarrison #TheBeatles #LiverpoolTheatre #ActorsWanted #CASA #NewPlay #December2025

items.text:
**034  Mini serial  wojenny 1940 – Szukamy mężczyzn na 30.11.25  ( casting on-line )**

 

Nasza Gliwicka Grupa Pasjonatów **‘’Grupa1940’’** poszukuje mężczyzn jako francuskich cywili uciekających przed atakami niemieckich żołnierzy. Mile widziane osoby z Gliwic lub okolic: Zabrza czy Katowic w różnym wieku. Zdjęcia próbne chcemy realizować w Gliwicach.

 

**Na wiosnę roku 2026 planujemy realizacje zdjęc do tego **projektu. Będziemy realizować mini serial oparty o wątki grupy okultystycznej ’’**Ahnenerbe’**’ która chce zdobyć słynne artefakty ale w tym ktoś im chce przeszkadzać. Będziemy też sukcesywnie dodawać inne ogłoszenia związane z tym projektem. Mile widziane zdjęcia aktualne. Na zdjęciu powyżej osoba będzie mieć podobny kostium.** **Umieszczone materiały są z naszej sesji.** Nie będzie to zlecenie płatne.**

 

Od 01.04.25 założyliśmy swój kanał na portalu youtube z filmami z naszych planów żeby można było zobaczyć jak to u nas wygląda od kuchni. 

 

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCE8KyfwpyFGzzwUDqdwy74g

 

**Nie będzie to zlecenie płatne.**

 

Więcej informacji na Priv

**Serial nie jest stworzony z sympatii do tej nazistowskiej organizacji lecz wynika to z samego scenariusza aby ukazał zbrodnie i sam fakt iż była w pełni zła. W produkcji znajdą się osoby, które będą chcieć walczyć i potępiać te wielkie zło jakim był nazizm. W oparciu o Dz.U.2017.0.2204 t.j. - Ustawa z dnia 6 czerwca 1997 r. - Kodeks karny,Art. 256 "Propagowanie faszyzmu lub innego ustroju totalitarnego lub nawoływanie domnienawiści", §3 - nie narusza prawa proponując przedmiot do celów historycznych lub kolekcjonerskich.**

items.text:
**012  Mini serial  wojenny 1940 – Szukamy ojca głównej bohaterki ( casting on-line )**

 

Nasza Gliwicka Grupa Pasjonatów ‘’Grupa1940’’ poszukuje mężczyzny do roli ojca głównej bohaterki. Najlepiej jakby kandydat miałby od **40 – 45 lat** o rudych włosach i bez zarostu, o określonych parametrach: **obwód w klatce 100- 105, obwód pasa 90/95 cm** i **wzrost: 175 -180** . Szukamy kogoś **z Gliwic lub okolic: Zabrze, Katowice** najdalej. Postać ta będzie nosić mundur polski podporucznika.Same zdjęcia będą realizowane na terenie Gliwic. Niestety nie zwracamy kosztów podróży. Postać mężczyzny pojawi się w pierwszym odcinku i zostanie zabita przez odział niemiecki. Pojawi się też w retrospekcji bitwy w 1919 roku z Bolszewikami gdzie zostanie ranny w nogę. Oczywiście mile widziane doświadczenie pracy z tekstem. Scenę wstępnie będziemy realizować na przełomie marca lub kwietnia.

 

**Na wiosnę roku 2026 planujemy realizacje zdjęc do tego **projektu. Od 01.04.25 założyliśmy swój kanał na portalu youtube z filmami z naszych planów żeby można było zobaczyć jak to u nas wygląda od kuchni. 

 

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCE8KyfwpyFGzzwUDqdwy74g

 

**Nie będzie to zlecenie płatne.**

 

Więcej informacji na Priv

**Serial nie jest stworzony z sympatii do tej nazistowskiej organizacji lecz wynika to z samego scenariusza aby ukazał zbrodnie i sam fakt iż była w pełni zła. W produkcji znajdą się osoby, które będą chcieć walczyć i potępiać te wielkie zło jakim był nazizm. W oparciu o Dz.U.2017.0.2204 t.j. - Ustawa z dnia 6 czerwca 1997 r. - Kodeks karny,Art. 256 "Propagowanie faszyzmu lub innego ustroju totalitarnego lub nawoływanie domnienawiści", §3 - nie narusza prawa proponując przedmiot do celów historycznych lub kolekcjonerskich.**

items.text:
KRAKÓW, TEATR NIEZALEŻNY

Szukam ludzi do spektaklu historyczno-poetyckiego, w stylu filmowym, epickim, opartym na życiorysach Tadeusza Borowskiego i Krzysztofa Kamila Baczyńskiego. Premiera przewidziana jest na marzec 2026 roku. Potrzebuję ludzi czujących epokę, poezję, niekoniecznie zawodowców. Poniżej lista postaci, do których szukam aktorów:
* Tadeusz (postać główna, pierwowzór - Tadeusz Borowski i Wincenty Gawron)
* Krzysztof (pierwowzór - K. K. Baczyński)
* Stary Doktor (pierwowzór - Janusz Korczak)
* Kapelan (pierwowzór - ksiądz Tiso)
* Bracia żydowscy Jakub i Izaak
* Roma (żona polskiego oficera)
* Pola (pierwowzór - Barbara Baczyńska)
* ''Święta'' (handlująca zrabowanymi kosztownościami)
* oficerowie hitlerowscy - Wolf i Jurgen

Chętne osoby zapraszam do kontaktu na priv. Pozdrawiam.

casting call 🚨

As a part of a school application I need to shoot a 3 minute bit.

The project will be about the exciting meeting of 2 friends outside of the prison one of them was in for two years.

I’m looking for a male actor who’d be taking the role of the friend who’s being released from jail, ideally mid - late 20’s, dark short hair (if someone here has a buzz cut that would be freakin amazing 😭) 

It’s a really low budget project but I’d be happy to give a small symbolic payment to a talented actor who’d be engaged in telling our story 💗

We're currently casting an international actor (age 25–36) for the main role of a short film shooting between November 2–3 in Warsaw.

The story is a black comedy about David, an immigrant spending his first christmas in another country with his girlfriend's family. 

❗️Requirements: Must know another language than polish and english, must communicate well in english aswell.

This is a non-profit project, but catering and transport are provided, along with a valuable creative experience in audiovisual storytelling.

If you're interested or know someone who might be, feel free to message me for more details. Looking forward to collaborating! 

🫶🏻For contact my email is : ikateon7@gmail.com

items.text:
· Title: This Side of Midnight

· Genre: Horror

· Logline: An eighteen-year-old girl must confront her inner demons, both real and metaphorical, as they test her to see if she is worthy of life itself after a brush with death.

· Role: Lilith — Female, late teens to early 20s

A newly eighteen-year-old struggling with severe depression and suicidal thoughts. Intelligent, introspective, and haunted by her inner world. The emotional core of the story.

Note: Lead role. Must be comfortable portraying intense emotional states.

Zera — Female, late teens to early 20s

Lilith’s best friend. Empathetic and determined, trying desperately to remind Lilith that she matters.

Dad — Male, 40s–50s (flexible)

A concerned father trying to reconnect with his daughter after finding her following a suicide attempt. Must convey deep emotion with subtlety.

Mom — Female, 40s–50s (flexible)

 A mother struggling to cope as her daughter begins to withdraw, stop eating, and lose hope.

Sibling — Any gender (preferably male), 10–15 (flexible)

Appears in one scene. No speaking lines, but must express strong emotion through facial expression and presence.

Cashier — Any gender/age

Background role, no speaking lines.

· Production Company: Cassidy Cheldelin — Writer, Director, Videographer, Editor
Jess Lange — Co-Director, Casting Director, Producer

· Production Type: Student Film

· Contact Information: Contact: Jess Lange — escapemindproductions@gmail.com
Instagram: @escapemind.productions 

· Run Time: Short (16 minutes)

· Compensation: Unpaid

· Union Status: Non-Union

· Audition Information: 

Format: Digital Submission

Please record a 1–2 minute monologue of your choice (preferably horror or drama) that demonstrates emotional depth. Include your name, age, preferred email & phone number, and desired role in the email. Name, age, and role for slate. 

Lilith Auditions: Monologue may be up to 5 minutes or the attached scene from the screenplay.

Dad Auditions: May choose to perform from the attached scene.

Submit to: escapemindproductions@gmail.com
Deadline: November 5, 11:59 PM (MST)

· Shooting Schedule: Mid-November (before Thanksgiving) table read, 11/8/25 at 12 (MST), location upon casting

· Filming Location: Black Forest, CO, 80908 & Colorado Springs, CO, North Academy Blvd.

· Project Description:

Two filmmakers are passionate about exploring mental health through the lens of horror. While this is not a professional production, we approach the project with deep respect and dedication to the craft. This Side of Midnight follows Lilith as she confronts her literal demons and manifestations of her struggles with mental illness, who test her will to live. When she ultimately fails, she is tragically taken, symbolizing the devastating reality of losing the battle against one’s own mind.

Lilith and Dad Scene 

Int. BEDROOM - MORNING

The screen flickers to her dad, shaking her awake

Dad

Lilith! Wake up! Please- Please, breathe please.

Lilith sits up suddenly, her breathing is chaotic, and she is in fear.

Her dad sighs in relief

Dad

Oh, thank god you are ok. I was about to call 911. What happened??

LILITH (studdering)

I- I don't know

She looks around the room, noticing the empty pill bottle next to her pillow, and she erratically shoves it further underneath so as not to let her dad see.

LILITH

Must've just been too much melatonin..

Dad

You scared the crap out of me and you're mother. Zera too.

Lilith looks defeated as her father sits more formally on her bed.

Dad

That reminds me, you should probably call her. She was worried sick about you.

LILITH

I will- I will do that.

Dad (in relief)

Good. You missed the bus. I have to go to work n' can't drive you- so have the day off.

LiLITH (under her breath)

T-Thanks.

DAD

A mental Health day- y'know? You deserve it.

Lilith's expression doesn't change. Her dad stands up and begins to put on his jacket

DAD

Let me know if you need anything, okay?
items.summary:
· Title: This Side of Midnight

· Genre: Horror

· Logline: An eighteen-year-old girl must confront her inner demons, both real and metaphorical, as they test her to see if she is worthy of life itself after a brush with death.

· Role: Lilith — Female, late teens to early 20s

A newly eighteen-year-old struggling with severe depression and suicidal thoughts. Intelligent, introspective, and haunted by her inner world. The emotional core of the story.

Note: Lead role. Must be comfortable portraying intense emotional states.

Zera — Female, late teens to early 20s

Lilith’s best friend. Empathetic and determined, trying desperately to remind Lilith that she matters.

Dad — Male, 40s–50s (flexible)

A concerned father trying to reconnect with his daughter after finding her following a suicide attempt. Must convey deep emotion with subtlety.

Mom — Female, 40s–50s (flexible)

 A mother struggling to cope as her daughter begins to withdraw, stop eating, and lose hope.

Sibling — Any gender (preferably male), 10–15 (flexible)

Appears in one scene. No speaking lines, but must express strong emotion through facial expression and presence.

Cashier — Any gender/age

Background role, no speaking lines.

items.text:
Für meinen No-Budget-Kurzfilm „Stella“ suche ich engagierte Schauspieler:innen aus der Umgebung von Nordhorn.

Catering, Showreelmaterial und eine familiäre, leidenschaftliche Drehatmosphäre sind selbstverständlich vorhanden.

Unterkunft und Gage können leider nicht übernommen werden.

Kurzbeschreibung des Films:

„Stella“ erzählt die Geschichte einer jungen Frau, die seit Jahren versucht, ihrem Bruder Felix aus der Patsche zu helfen – koste es, was es wolle.

Als Felix in ernste Geldsorgen gerät, überschreitet Stella Grenzen, um ihn zu retten. Doch als sie Nick kennenlernt, prallen Loyalität und Liebe aufeinander – und alles droht zu eskalieren.

Ein emotionales Drama über Verantwortung, Geschwisterliebe und das Loslassen.

🪞 Kurzbeschreibung des Films:

„Stella“ erzählt die Geschichte einer jungen Frau, die seit Jahren versucht, ihrem Bruder Felix aus der Patsche zu helfen – koste es, was es wolle.

Als Felix in ernste Geldsorgen gerät, überschreitet Stella Grenzen, um ihn zu retten. Doch als sie Nick kennenlernt, prallen Loyalität und Liebe aufeinander – und alles droht zu eskalieren.

Ein emotionales Drama über Verantwortung, Geschwisterliebe und das Loslassen.

⸻

🎭 Gesuchte Rollen:

🔹 Felix (ca. 20–25 Jahre)

– Boxkenntnisse oder Grundfitness erwünscht

– Ruhiger, leicht muskulöser Typ

– Stelllas Bruder, gerät in finanzielle Schwierigkeiten

🔹 Jan (ca. 20–25 Jahre)

– Bester Freund von Felix

– Ebenfalls sportlich / Boxerfahrung von Vorteil

🔹 Kleiner Felix (ca. 6 Jahre)

– Für Rückblenden

– Verspielt, offen, gerne erste Kameraerfahrung

🔹 Mutter von Stella (ca. 30–35 Jahre)

– Für Rückblenden

– Warmherzig, sympathisch 

🔹 Boxer / Trainingsgegner (20–30 Jahre)

– Kurzer Auftritt in Trainingsszenen

– Sportlich, authentische Boxbewegungen

⸻

📍 Drehort: Nordhorn 

🎥 Drehzeitraum: Jan/Feb

💡 Art: No-Budget-Projekt (Catering & Showreel inklusive)

🎬 **Filmprojekt sucht weibliche Darstellerinnen (Raum München)**

Für ein unabhängiges Fan-/Action-Filmprojekt im Stil von *Assassin’s Creed*, *COD* und Fantasy-Elementen suchen wir noch **motivierte Darstellerinnen** für verschiedene Szenen.
📍 Drehort: Raum München / Grafing
💡 Kein kommerzielles Projekt – auf **TFP-Basis (Time for Project)**
👗 Kostüme & Requisiten werden gestellt
🎥 Erfahrung ist kein Muss – wichtig sind **Teamgeist, Zuverlässigkeit und Spaß am Spielen vor der Kamera**

Bei Interesse einfach kurz per PN melden – ich sende gern nähere Infos zum Projekt.

sharedPost.text:
✨ A Smile for Christmas – A song that brings warmth and a smile.
When the world outside is wrapped in snow, the pan flute tells of that special moment when a simple smile means more than any gift.
Gentle tones that touch the heart – a musical light in the quiet, festive season.

A song that reminds us: Christmas doesn’t begin under the tree, but in a sincere smile. 🎄😊

A Smile for Christmas – Ein Lied, das Wärme und ein lächeln schenkt.
Wenn draußen die Welt in Schnee gehüllt ist, erzählt die Panflöte von jenem besonderen Moment, in dem ein einfaches Lächeln mehr bedeutet als jedes Geschenk.
Sanfte Klänge, die das Herz berühren – ein musikalisches Licht in der stillen, festlichen Zeit.

Ein Song, der daran erinnert: Weihnachten beginnt nicht unter dem Baum, sondern in einem ehrlichen Lächeln. 🎄😊

Composer : Pan Hope (Horst Peter Zoll)
Artist : PAN HOPE #musik #christmastime #newmusic

✨ Estill Level 1 und 2 Kurse – Belting, Introduction Workshops, Anwendungskurse, Artikulation, Zertifizierungskurse – Jetzt anmelden! ✨

Plane jetzt dein Stimmtraining für 2026 – noch gibt es freie Plätze! Ob Level 1 oder Level 2, Online oder vor Ort in Frankfurt am Main, für jede*n ist das passende Angebot dabei.

In unseren Kursen lernst du unter anderem:
🎶 Die Figuren des Estill Voice Trainings
🔄 Verschiedene Arten der Stimmlippenschwingung – von Belting über Operngesang bis Country Western
💪 Wie anatomische Strukturen des Vokaltraktes und des Körpers zusammenwirken
🎤 Störungsmöglichkeiten erkennen und die Stimme gezielt befreien
🗣️ Artikulation und gezielte Anwendung für verschiedene Gesangsstile
📜 Vorbereitung auf Zertifizierungskurse

Gewinne mehr Überblick, Stimmkontrolle und Stimmgesundheit, um deine Stimme vielfältig und gesund einzusetzen.

📅 Sichere dir jetzt deinen Platz für 2026!
👉 Melde dich jetzt an und erlebe, wie Wissenschaft deine Stimme hörbar verbessert!

items.text:
📸 2 STATISTER SØGES TIL FOTOOPTAGELSER I KOLDING

Pga sygdom mangler jeg 2 statister til en fotooptagelse på Comwell Kolding i morgen mandag den 20. oktober. Billederne skal bruges i markedsføringsøjemed for Comwell Hotels – primært til promovering af møder og konferencer.

Køn: Mænd og kvinder

Alder: 35 år og opefter

Hvornår: Mandag den 20. oktober 2025

Tid: Kl. 8.30–16.00

Sted: Comwell Kolding, Skovbrynet 1, 6000 Kolding

Din rolle: Mødedeltager og/eller forretningsrejsende

Dresscode: Casual business 

Forplejning: Morgenmad, frokost og eftermiddagsforplejning er inkluderet

Der vil være stylist og makeupartist til stede, som hjælper med et naturligt og professionelt look på dagen. Dog skal alle statister selv medbringe 2-3 sæt tøj jfr dresscode: Casual business.

Det er vigtigt, at du selv kan komme til og fra location, og at du selv står for transportomkostninger.

Honorar

Som tak for din medvirken modtager du et gavekort til Comwell Hotels på 1.500 kr. Bemærk, at værdien indberettes som B-indkomst til SKAT i henhold til gældende lovgivning.

Er du frisk?

så send hurtigst muligt en mail til LN@comwell.com med følgende:

• Fulde navn og kontaktoplysninger

• Alder

• Et eller flere nyere billeder i fuld profil (uden filter)

Billederne viser stemninger fra tidligere shoots og bruges kun som eksempel.

SOCIAL MEDIA CASTING CALLS 📞
We’re on the lookout for a confident, camera-ready person to become the face of multiple businesses on social media — creating fun, engaging videos that represent local brands across Yorkshire 🎥✨
If you’ve got energy, personality, and love being on camera, this is your chance to shine! We need someone who can start filming immediately. 🌍
📍 Location: Yorkshire
🗓️ Starting Filming: This Wednesday!
💰 Pay: Competitive (you’ll love it!)
You’ll be working with a creative marketing team that produces high-quality social content for some of the most exciting local names.
👉 Think you’ve got what it takes and are available this week?

Drop us a message

items.text:
Hi, hello, Sat Sri Akaal, I’m Sukhmanjeet, A 16 year old aspiring actor from Australia, who will be taking a giant dive (preferably from a plane) into acting.

it should be clear that I am 16 ALTHOUGH, I have a beard, which by itself sounds very anticlimactic… BUT  🙂‍↕️ it gives me a wider range of characters to portray 😎 (depending on length and gritty-ness) sometimes people mistake me as a 27 year old with my little sister as my child and it’s fun to act that out 😅 fond memories.

I’m roughly 182 cm tall (abt 5’11 3/4), 
weigh 85 (I do plan on becoming fitter and losing weight), 
My Entinicty is south Asian/ Indian (Sikh),
Hair: black and almost shoulder length
Hair-Style: to be a wolf but as of now still growing it out 🤞
Eyes: brown
My chest size is roughly 107 cm and my hips are 97 cm

I decided to take drama classes last year, fell in love, and have focused on many different roles always pushing for roles in different projects, I’ve volunteered to act in student’s film assignments just for the experience. The way I see it, every chance to act is a step closer to getting really good at what I want to do. 😁
 
I’m genuinly so grateful for everyone’s who have been with me, my teachers, my friends, directors and I could not be less excited to meet more amazing people such as yourself, so if your an actor, creator or a director,
Let’s connect and possibly get the chance to make something incredible together‼️

Email: sukh.singh7t@gmail.com
Number: 0421505765
Or you could reach me here on Facebook 😄.

items.text:
Casting Call for Scotland Based Actors

I really am serious about this project and do require some heads to fill.

Maya (Playing Age 22-27) Maya is a scared girl who was emotionally and mentally tormented by the brutal government. F

Beta 2 (Playing Age 20-25) Beta 2 is the youngest of the Betas. F

Hey cut the chit chat, the leader is coming.

Beta 7 (Playing Age 25-40) The Betas are one note characters but follow direct orders. M or F

BETA 7
Can’t believe we’ve been dragged out into the middle of nowhere just to hunt down two thieves. 

Filming Location: Leven, Kirkcaldy and Glenrothes 

For more information 
cjnicoll476@gmail.com or DM me.

Casting Call for Scotland Based Actors

I really am serious about this project and do require some heads to fill.

Maya (Playing Age 22-27) Maya is a scared girl who was emotionally and mentally tormented by the brutal government. F

Beta 2 (Playing Age 20-25) Beta 2 is the youngest of the Betas. F

Hey cut the chit chat, the leader is coming.

Beta 7 (Playing Age 25-40) The Betas are one note characters but follow direct orders. M or F

BETA 7
Can’t believe we’ve been dragged out into the middle of nowhere just to hunt down two thieves. 

Filming Location: Leven, Kirkcaldy and Glenrothes 

For more information 
cjnicoll476@gmail.com or DM me.

items.text:
Been cooking up a lot of projects behind the scenes and this is the most recent! 

Currently casting for a new short, working title 'The Heist', filming in Northern Quarter, Manchester!

In 1994, a duo of thieves, interrogated after a heist gone wrong, find their fates decided by the value of their mysterious stolen item 🪙

STUDENT FILM, SHOOTING IN MANCHESTER, EARLY NOV, UNPAID

THE INTERROGATOR

mid 30s. 

Stoic but becomes fascinated with the two thieves' stories. 

RAY

20 - 30

Confident, in charge and narcissistic. Takes the lead within the duo

NICK

18 - 25

new to the crime world, scruffy and erratic. Intimidated by Ray.

Within plenty of space to collaborate, build and bring your own energy and flair to the story and the characters, this may be a good opportunity for upcoming actors building their portfolio and looking for experience! 

We are currently looking for self tape auditions

If interested please message me here or email izzyhambury1@gmail.com

for further details

🎄Lapland 2025 Christmas Season - Character Elves (Noisy Nod, Speedy Sam, Tricky Dicky, Green elves)

Want to learn how to transition from doing music into Acting?

**📍 𝐋𝐨𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧:** HOME Mcr, 𝟐 𝐓𝐨𝐧𝐲 𝐖𝐢𝐥𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐏𝐥, 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐌𝟏𝟓 𝟒𝐅𝐍

This is not just another event; it’s your chance to connect with a dynamic community of actors, directors, producers, and writers who share your passion!
Networking is an essential part of our industry, so don’t let this opportunity pass you by.
Tickets are available at this link. 

[https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239](https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239)

Also, if you're looking for captivating headshots or seeking to refresh your current images, the excellent Lisa Barton from Lisa Barton photography will be joining us at the event to showcase her incredible work!

items.text:
Hey there! 👋🏻😃

I’m Freya Tingley — an Australian actress born and raised in Perth. I started acting at 14, taking weekly classes with a dream of one day building a career in Hollywood.

Bit by bit, I booked short films, found a local agent, and put together a demo reel — all steps that helped me make the leap to LA just before turning 18. Not long after, I landed my first major role as a series regular on Netflix’s Hemlock Grove, followed by Once Upon a Time, Jersey Boys, and DOTA: Dragon’s Blood.

Of course, it wasn’t all smooth sailing and the journey had its pitfalls and huge learning curves along the way. But those ups and the downs gave me something valuable; an understanding of what works, what doesn’t and the exact steps to take to keep moving forward. 

Most acting schools don’t teach how to build a career — they’ll say “get an agent,” or “network: it’s all about who you know!” - but there’s never a clear road map, or step-by-step plan to help you to make progress, no matter where you’re at that.

I’m building a community for actors who want a clear game plan, strategy, and support to level up and turn their goals into reality.

Come hang out with us! I’d love to meet you, hear your story, and help you move closer to your dreams.

👉 Join The Business of Acting www.skool.com/the-business-of-acting-9301/about?ref=387a46092b6b412b82c1a78a4c1a240e

items.summary:
Hey there! 👋🏻😃

I’m Freya Tingley — an Australian actress born and raised in Perth. I started acting at 14, taking weekly classes with a dream of one day building a career in Hollywood.

Bit by bit, I booked short films, found a local agent, and put together a demo reel — all steps that helped me make the leap to LA just before turning 18. Not long after, I landed my first major role as a series regular on Netflix’s Hemlock Grove, followed by Once Upon a Time, Jersey Boys, and DOTA: Dragon’s Blood.

Of course, it wasn’t all smooth sailing and the journey had its pitfalls and huge learning curves along the way. But those ups and the downs gave me something valuable; an understanding of what works, what doesn’t and the exact steps to take to keep moving forward. 

Most acting schools don’t teach how to build a career — they’ll say “get an agent,” or “network: it’s all about who you know!” - but there’s never a clear road map, or step-by-step plan to help you to make progress, no matter where you’re at that.

I’m building a community for actors who want a clear game plan, strategy, and support to level up and turn their goals into reality.

Come hang out with us! I’d love to meet you, hear your story, and help you move closer to your dreams.

👉 Join The Business of Acting www.skool.com/the-business-of-acting-9301/about?ref=387a46092b6b412b82c1a78a4c1a240e

See you there! 😃
— Freya

Dream & Dazzle Parties is growing and on the lookout for more energetic, reliable, and imaginative performers to join our fun, dynamic team! We predominantly provide princess performers for children’s parties across London and surrounding areas, but we also offer other entertainment opportunities so we would love to hear from you if you meet our requirements! 🌟 

We’re especially keen to hear from people with:
🎭 Performing or teaching experience 
🎉 Experience working with children and/or leading workshops for children 
🚗 A driver’s license (a bonus but not essential)
💫 A passion for creating unforgettable memories for families

We believe kids should see performers who reflect the wonderfully diverse world they live in- so we warmly welcome applications from performers of all backgrounds, particularly those from underrepresented communities.

If you think you would make a great addition to our team, we’d love to hear from you🌟
📩 Please send your CV and a recent headshot to janelle@dreamanddazzle.co.uk

# CASTING CALL - PIERROT

**A UBC STUDENT SHORT FILM**

*A desperate woman on the verge of eviction, whose earnings as a sex worker mean survival, finds herself trapped in a performance of desperation and self-erasure.*

## **[MISS LEFOU]** *20 to 30 years old; all ethnicities; woman - Lead*
## [GWEN] *35 to 55 years old; all ethnicities; woman - Actor*
## [MAN] *30 to 50 years old; all ethnicities; man - Actor*

*Producer: Zev Lemke*

*Director: Julianne Pascua*
*Writer: Julianne Pascua*
*Auditions: Self-tape + In-person callback date *
*Shoot Dates: December 6-8 (3-day shoot)*
*Location: Greater Vancouver + surrounding areas*

*Callbacks: November 6th, 17:00-20:00 OR November 9th, 18:00-23:00*

**SUBMISSION DEADLINE: NOVEMBER 2ND, 2025**

**Hello, Open casting call with no experience required!**
Pierrot is a UBC short film created by students, so unfortunately, this is an unpaid position.
Given the subject matter of the script**,** we will have an intimacy coordinator on set**,** but we would also like actors who feel comfortable performing intimate scenes. 

All submissions and casting instructions can be found in the link to each casting call in the form of a GOOGLE FORM:

GWEN - [https://forms.gle/WSM1N7b7ci5gUVwo7](https://forms.gle/WSM1N7b7ci5gUVwo7)

Thank you
* Zev and the Pierrot Team

This is a great opportunity to gain on-set experience, expand your portfolio, and be part of a fun and ambitious student film! 🎥✨

items.text:
📣🎬 CASTING CALL - Short Period Drama 

We are casting for The Stuntman, a 3-minute period drama made as part of our final year at UWE Bristol. The film will be shot in Bristol in the week commencing 10th November 2025 (exact dates TBC). This is a student project, unpaid, but with expenses covered. The film is intended for university showcase and festival submission.

Story:
Set in 1920s Wiltshire, The Stuntman follows Ed Morris, a small-town silent cinema owner fighting to keep his theatre alive as the arrival of sound threatens to change film forever. With his fiancée Alice by his side, Ed stages one last ambitious stunt in the hope of saving his cinema - and their livelihood. A warm yet bittersweet drama about determination, passion and the march of technological change.

Roles:
Ed Morris (Lead, 28)
Charming, intelligent, and hardworking. Outwardly confident, but hiding a quiet desperation as he struggles to keep silent film alive. Needs strong screen presence and subtle emotional depth.

Alice Fardon (Lead, 22–23)
Ed’s fiancée. Feisty, loyal, and practical. She supports his dreams but occasionally shows frustration at his all-consuming determination.

Community Extras
Townsfolk gathering to watch Ed’s big stunt. A mix of ages. Families, workers and individuals. To capture the atmosphere of a 1920s local community.

Apply by: 1st November 2025
To Apply: Please send a headshot, CV (or Spotlight/Mandy link), and any showreel/self-tape to: Scarlet2.Gerry@live.uwe.ac.uk

Please include in email subject: THE STUNTMAN & NAME

STUDENT FILM, SHOOTING IN MANCHESTER, EARLY NOV, UNPAID

THE INTERROGATOR

mid 30s. 

Stoic but becomes fascinated with the two thieves' stories. 

RAY

20 - 30

Confident, in charge and narcissistic. Takes the lead within the duo

NICK

18 - 25

new to the crime world, scruffy and erratic. Intimidated by Ray.

Within plenty of space to collaborate, build and bring your own energy and flair to the story and the characters, this may be a good opportunity for upcoming actors building their portfolio and looking for experience! 

We are currently looking for self tape auditions

If interested please message me here or email izzyhambury1@gmail.com

for further details

items.text:
# (Paid) Casting for George Fox University Student Film, (Hillsboro, Oregon)

We are a group of George Fox students shooting a short film at the Airplane Home for our Location Production class, looking for a total of three non-union actors.

Project Title: Clearing The Air

Location: Airplane Home: 15270 SW Holly Hill Rd, Hillsboro, OR 97123

Safety Considerations: Dress for potential rain and cold weather. Several cats roam around the area, so be weary if you have any allergies. The actor that plays Jean will hold a non functional prop firearm.

 Shoot Dates: 10/28/2025 and 10/30/2025, 2:00PM - 9:00PM

Age Requirement: 18 and over

Pay: 50$ per day

You will receive a collection of your scenes to include in your reel.

Synopsis: Lost in the woods, siblings Gertie and Hudson come upon an airplane containing valuables. The sister aims to ransack the plane, while her brother urges her against it. Upon the return of the airplane’s resident, Jean, the sister attempts to escape with her spoils by attacking Jean from behind while her brother serves as a distraction. Her plan is thwarted by Jean, who catches her in the act, and Hudson, who reveals her presence and forces her to return what she stole. Once the two parties agree to part ways, it is revealed that Jean is a fugitive with a reward for her capture, worth more than anything the siblings could’ve stolen.

Character Breakdown

(Antagonist) Jean: A perceptive older woman with a soft face but a hardened demeanor, a criminal past, and a lifetime of secrets behind her eyes.

Age: The character is meant to be in her early sixties, but her age isn't a strict guideline.

(Protagonist) Hudson: A thoughtful late teen with dark hair, an anxious posture, and a subdued retro rock styling, who has a tendency to let others walk over him.

He is the younger brother to Gertie.

"Think William Miller in Almost Famous but more frazzled and sarcastic."

Age: Roughly 18-19

(Protagonist) Gertie: An outdoorsy, has-it-all-together college girl with a “Karen Carpenter” fashion sense, a hidden impulsive nature, and a proclivity toward not seeing beyond her own scope.

Age: Around 20-21 years old

Audition sides are in the link below. Please record your auditions and send them to Bronson Revilla at brevilla21@georgefox.edu.

items.summary:
# (Paid) Casting for George Fox University Student Film, (Hillsboro, Oregon)

We are a group of George Fox students shooting a short film at the Airplane Home for our Location Production class, looking for a total of three non-union actors.

Project Title: Clearing The Air

Location: Airplane Home: 15270 SW Holly Hill Rd, Hillsboro, OR 97123

Safety Considerations: Dress for potential rain and cold weather. Several cats roam around the area, so be weary if you have any allergies. The actor that plays Jean will hold a non functional prop firearm.

 Shoot Dates: 10/28/2025 and 10/30/2025, 2:00PM - 9:00PM

Age Requirement: 18 and over

Pay: 50$ per day

You will receive a collection of your scenes to include in your reel.

Synopsis: Lost in the woods, siblings Gertie and Hudson come upon an airplane containing valuables. The sister aims to ransack the plane, while her brother urges her against it. Upon the return of the airplane’s resident, Jean, the sister attempts to escape with her spoils by attacking Jean from behind while her brother serves as a distraction. Her plan is thwarted by Jean, who catches her in the act, and Hudson, who reveals her presence and forces her to return what she stole. Once the two parties agree to part ways, it is revealed that Jean is a fugitive with a reward for her capture, worth more than anything the siblings could’ve stolen.

Character Breakdown

(Antagonist) Jean: A perceptive older woman with a soft face but a hardened demeanor, a criminal past, and a lifetime of secrets behind her eyes.

Age: The character is meant to be in her early sixties, but her age isn't a strict guideline.

(Protagonist) Hudson: A thoughtful late teen with dark hair, an anxious posture, and a subdued retro rock styling, who has a tendency to let others walk over him.

He is the younger brother to Gertie.

"Think William Miller in Almost Famous but more frazzled and sarcastic."

Age: Roughly 18-19

(Protagonist) Gertie: An outdoorsy, has-it-all-together college girl with a “Karen Carpenter” fashion sense, a hidden impulsive nature, and a proclivity toward not seeing beyond her own scope.

Age: Around 20-21 years old

Audition sides are in the link below. Please record your auditions and send them to Bronson Revilla at brevilla21@georgefox.edu.

[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JdV5_ZnMYF6723lCAGBG3bluhEtj3u9prGwzw-Q1BcY/edit?usp=sharing](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JdV5_ZnMYF6723lCAGBG3bluhEtj3u9prGwzw-Q1BcY/edit?usp=sharing)

items.text:
**CASTING CALL – Gaunt Man / Doctor (Dual Role) in Short Film *****The Damned Spot***

**Production Title:** *The Damned Spot*
**Company:** SWRCO Studios / Racetothefinishline Studios
**Location:** Atlanta, GA
**Union Status:** Non-Union
**Compensation:** $200 flat rate (2 half-days)
**Role: Gaunt Man / Doctor (Male, 40s–80s)**

**Character Description:**
This is a dual-performance role. The **Doctor** appears grounded, calm, and professional — a clinician trying to reassure his patient. The **Gaunt Man** is his nightmarish double: unsettling, skeletal in presence, and haunting. The shift between the two is central to the film’s psychological horror.

**Requirements:**
* Male, age range 40–85
* Ability to portray both a grounded, realistic character and a chilling, silent presence
* Strong facial expression and physical control — much of the horror relies on stillness and presence
* Comfortable with light makeup (pale complexion, under-eye work) and basic VFX markers
**Filming Commitment:**
* 2 Half-Days
* $200 flat rate
**To Apply:**

Please submit:
* Headshot and resume (or reel, if available)
* Brief note about prior experience in psychological drama or horror
* Contact information

Send submissions to: **studio@swrco.us**
**Deadline:** **10-24-2025**
